This paper focuses on improving observability of Dockerized Java applications, which is a topic related to distributed systems and cloud computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also involves automated transformations of Docker configuration files, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper deals with injecting additional modules into the production application, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses fault injection, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY).
